bug.short_desc: search only in - needs more work

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 4642 "search only in" example
(version 0.11.1rc1) gives a false suggestion (in case of files) on where the lookup will be made. In case a file is opened in BUI, it suggests the search to be performed only in that file, while the actual search is later constrained by the directory with the given file. This is wrong.
